  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a blender or food processor, combine plums, smoked paprika, garlic, and cilantro. Blend until smooth.",
    "Brush the tomato halves with olive oil and season with salt and black pepper.",
    "Grill the tomatoes for 3-4 minutes per side or until slightly charred.",
    "In a small saucepan, combine the plum sauce and balsamic vinegar. Bring to a simmer over medium heat.",
    "Serve the grilled tomatoes with the warm plum sauce spooned over the top."
